{"id": "ChIJR6XJs1p_hYAR1bL7Xq_9FII", "rating": 4.9, "userRatingCount": 234, "displayName": {"text": "ChaHalo 茶话弄 - Berkeley", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJR6XJs1p_hYAR1bL7Xq_9FII/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxdE9VTTFUWE5XZDB0bGVURlJORFpwT1Y5TWVFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Beautiful branding and friendly staff. It was a little difficult to hear the staff speak, but I really enjoyed the milk tea and will definitely return！", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Beautiful branding and friendly staff. It was a little difficult to hear the staff speak, but I really enjoyed the milk tea and will definitely return！", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Michael Li", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111541299734080395898/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyEf_6JlNFVFka3Mt6luAxGc-EGkrXDa1Kw7lF1Dk944jrhQA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-12T08:48:33.224920519Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxdE9VTTFUWE5XZDB0bGVURlJORFpwT1Y5TWVFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxdE9VTTFUWE5XZDB0bGVURlJORFpwT1Y5TWVFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f5ab3c9a547:0x8214fdaf5efbb2d5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJR6XJs1p_hYAR1bL7Xq_9FII/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOV01qVlBZWGhCT1V0dVVYUllTeloyU1hSaVlVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Decided to escape from my daily coffee run and switch to boba for a day. I first tried Chahalo in Vancouver and really liked it, so I stopped by their new Berkeley location while waiting for some friends nearby.\n\nOrdering is done through a kiosk near the entrance, and it didn’t look like they were taking orders at the counter yet. Thankfully, it wasn’t busy when I got there, so there was only a short wait.\n\nI ordered the Jasmine Milk Tea with 30% sugar and less ice. My drink came out pretty quickly, and they have large screens that show the status of every order, which makes pickup easy. There are also good amount of small tables if you want to sit down and chat.\n\nThe Jasmine Milk Tea was just as good as I remembered. The last time I had it hot, but it was equally enjoyable iced. The jasmine flavor is fragrant without being overpowering, and it pairs really well with the milk. After a few sips, I was already wishing I had ordered a large.\n\nOverall, I really enjoyed it. Their tea quality stands out, and it is easy to see why I came back. I would happily order from them again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Decided to escape from my daily coffee run and switch to boba for a day. I first tried Chahalo in Vancouver and really liked it, so I stopped by their new Berkeley location while waiting for some friends nearby.\n\nOrdering is done through a kiosk near the entrance, and it didn’t look like they were taking orders at the counter yet. Thankfully, it wasn’t busy when I got there, so there was only a short wait.\n\nI ordered the Jasmine Milk Tea with 30% sugar and less ice. My drink came out pretty quickly, and they have large screens that show the status of every order, which makes pickup easy. There are also good amount of small tables if you want to sit down and chat.\n\nThe Jasmine Milk Tea was just as good as I remembered. The last time I had it hot, but it was equally enjoyable iced. The jasmine flavor is fragrant without being overpowering, and it pairs really well with the milk. After a few sips, I was already wishing I had ordered a large.\n\nOverall, I really enjoyed it. Their tea quality stands out, and it is easy to see why I came back. I would happily order from them again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "CoffeeRunner", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113758384643168674447/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKqpq-CuvZxtq6wnd1_8HQoAAXZwVSNghejgqdI5gsBsfgwYg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-02T17:03:06.368138104Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOV01qVlBZWGhCT1V0dVVYUllTeloyU1hSaVlVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOV01qVlBZWGhCT1V0dVVYUllTeloyU1hSaVlVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f5ab3c9a547:0x8214fdaf5efbb2d5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJR6XJs1p_hYAR1bL7Xq_9FII/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xrd1kyWjFXbk53WVhkSE9ERklTbmR1VVdOMWJXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Just tried this newly opened tea shop located in downtown Berkeley! The interior has such an elegant Eastern aesthetic, creating a cozy and unique atmosphere. Every drink I tried was amazing.\nI definitely recommend ordering full sugar, and the creamy top is an absolute must-try.🧋✨", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Just tried this newly opened tea shop located in downtown Berkeley! The interior has such an elegant Eastern aesthetic, creating a cozy and unique atmosphere. Every drink I tried was amazing.\nI definitely recommend ordering full sugar, and the creamy top is an absolute must-try.🧋✨", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Fiamma Liu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114656110013933802929/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQ4VFFF3QoYznANGSOWfK1sUEh_bIvgS0kPFLecSrYVSBi8g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-01T16:19:26.152811414Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xrd1kyWjFXbk53WVhkSE9ERklTbmR1VVdOMWJXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xrd1kyWjFXbk53WVhkSE9ERklTbmR1VVdOMWJXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f5ab3c9a547:0x8214fdaf5efbb2d5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJR6XJs1p_hYAR1bL7Xq_9FII/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21RNFVrUnlaMW80VG1OSE1WbElVbms1VWtsalQyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Best milk tea in SF/Bay area. Tried multiple flavors and got different surprises - the osmanthus milk tea is my favorite, which gives me the pic in mind of ancient eastern culture, very impressive. While the grape flavored milk tea brought the fresh feeling just like the fresh air of a sunshine morning right after a big rain.\n\nI could see the owner spent a lot of effort and energy on designing the decorations, mixed style of eastern culture and modern style.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Best milk tea in SF/Bay area. Tried multiple flavors and got different surprises - the osmanthus milk tea is my favorite, which gives me the pic in mind of ancient eastern culture, very impressive. While the grape flavored milk tea brought the fresh feeling just like the fresh air of a sunshine morning right after a big rain.\n\nI could see the owner spent a lot of effort and energy on designing the decorations, mixed style of eastern culture and modern style.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Wei Chang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106860602881983271745/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImhOOnn0niY6G8BZzvHr4H6LYSyu6y0_vKTYlP7pykarD_lw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-04T09:34:37.960059419Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21RNFVrUnlaMW80VG1OSE1WbElVbms1VWtsalQyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21RNFVrUnlaMW80VG1OSE1WbElVbms1VWtsalQyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f5ab3c9a547:0x8214fdaf5efbb2d5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJR6XJs1p_hYAR1bL7Xq_9FII/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sWVdHMDVWbmRQTkdkU1YwRkdha3BLZW5jNGNVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Stopped by ChaHalo and was genuinely impressed. The shop is beautifully designed, and the attention to detail shows from the decor to the packaging. The staff were friendly and worked quickly despite a steady flow of customers. It’s great to see a new tea spot.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Stopped by ChaHalo and was genuinely impressed. The shop is beautifully designed, and the attention to detail shows from the decor to the packaging. The staff were friendly and worked quickly despite a steady flow of customers. It’s great to see a new tea spot.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "C J", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101094868603544741932/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIOexO8E1EMLl3SAHD423ba1Iz-y_rQHbz8z4a-lcoCPpgEkA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-01T00:11:40.455724627Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sWVdHMDVWbmRQTkdkU1YwRkdha3BLZW5jNGNVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sWVdHMDVWbmRQTkdkU1YwRkdha3BLZW5jNGNVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f5ab3c9a547:0x8214fdaf5efbb2d5"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJR6XJs1p_hYAR1bL7Xq_9FII/photos/AWCwydh4l1Pit1slXfeyZouJLQPFe6GRUYwVq0Y7wR8Az3ckRxn3a4hFn1YWifb9k1pjPLg-C6ZdoDHUYVUjJ3X0CMZYXCqJ1uTldtaCuVlyKen4F2afh6MhGOGZAXwhOqGX15SIcunJ7OvtNV7j5jlSGrOiOfd0w2cR8kYi_p2_HQfM7cGHC-y2UdFoN8puocBaoEdIp_1_TpxHbrKAc53tF_5Dq9yba0pxj_GTh2s6dUm3QFXsXcZms_zuh7ssMIfCuY9KboLk14t2-2nqppggADGuHb42KoTqyoVUCR0aJOPOr_5EsD2ae2QUrKaECb9SB1ng4pxglOr-ToHkU7ful8iwzVzOxoW-ZvXlfFC1J_sa0XjhJ7lfBNORoFDjMxOSNDLl5oaNwtfS0CUhsc55XfhkTLsGIdk6xZTc2LOHixs1kiIV-dyLO9_PMl-hDw", "widthPx": 1207, "heightPx": 679, "authorAttributions": [{"displayNam